<?xml version="1.0" standalone="yes"?>
<root>
  <View view_layout="vertical" name="parent">
    <BorderView view_layout="horizontal" >
      <TextView value="Available Improvement Points:" font="LARGE" layout_borders="Rect(2,0,3,0)" name="remaining_ip_lbl"/>
      <HLayoutSpacer/>
      <TextView value="100000000" font="LARGE" layout_borders="Rect(1,0,3,0)" name="remaining_ip" />
      <Button name="Accept" label="Save" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)"/>
      <Button name="Quit" label="Close" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)"/>
    </BorderView>
    <View view_layout="horizontal" name="top_line">
      <BorderView view_layout="horizontal"  layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="main" width_group_owner="parent" >
        <Button name="suggest_ip" label="Suggested IP distribution" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
      </BorderView>
      <BorderView view_layout="vertical"  layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="right_group" width_group_owner="parent" >
        <TextView value="" name="status" layout_borders="Rect(2,2,2,2)" min_size="Point(0,0)" max_size="Point(10000,10000)"/>
      </BorderView>
    </View>
    <View view_layout="horizontal" >
      <BorderView view_layout="vertical" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="main" width_group_owner="parent">
        <ScrollView v_scrollbar_mode="auto" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" >
          <ScrollViewChild view_layout="vertical" name="scroller" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
            <Button label="Abilities" name="abilities" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" name="abilities_view" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" >
            </BorderView>
            <Button label="Body" name="body" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" name="body_view" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
            </BorderView>
            <Button label="Melee" name="melee" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" name="melee_view" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
            </BorderView>
            <Button name="misc" label="Misc Weapons" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" name="misc_view" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
            </BorderView>
            <Button name="ranged" label="Ranged" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" name="ranged_view" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
            </BorderView>
            <Button name="speed" label="Speed" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" name="speed_view" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
            </BorderView>
            <Button name="traderepair" label="Trade &amp; Repair" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" name="traderepair_view" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
            </BorderView>
            <Button name="nanoaiding" label="Nano &amp; Aiding" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" name="nanoaiding_view" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
            </BorderView>
            <Button name="spying" label="Spying" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" name="spying_view" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
            </BorderView>
            <Button name="navigation" label="Navigation" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="buttons" width_group_owner="parent"/>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" name="navigation_view" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
            </BorderView>
            <VLayoutSpacer/>
          </ScrollViewChild>
        </ScrollView>
      </BorderView>
      <View view_layout="vertical"  layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" width_group="right_group" width_group_owner="parent" name="info_area">
        <ViewSelector name="infoselect">
          <BorderView name="inittext" view_layout="vertical">
            <TextView value="The Skill System
            
Your skills define what you can do, and how good you are at it. Items have skill requirements for using and/or equipping them, nano programs have skill requirements for uploading and executing them.

At each level your character is awarded a certain amount of Improvement Points (IPs). These IPs allow you to raise the skills that in turn allow you to use better weapons, armour, nano-programs and other general equipment.

It is not possible to maximize all the skills, as you are not awarded enough IPs to do so; therefore you have to concentrate on the areas of most use to your character.

If you are new to Anarchy Online we suggest you use the &#8216;Suggested IP Distribution&#8217; option to allocate your skills. This option will be available to you until level 20.

More detailed information on the skill view can be found in the help system. You can access this by clicking the &#8216;?&#8217; in the upper right corner of this window." 
 layout_borders="Rect(2,2,2,2)" max_size="Point(10000,-1)" feature_flags="TVF_MULTILINE|TVF_WORD_WRAP|TVF_ALLOW_TEXT_SELECTION"/>
            <VLayoutSpacer/>
          </BorderView>
          <View name="info" view_layout="vertical">
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
              <ViewSelector name="groupselect">
                <View view_layout="vertical" name="abilities_group" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)" >
                </View>
                <View view_layout="vertical" name="body_group" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
                </View>
                <View view_layout="vertical" name="melee_group" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
                </View>
                <View view_layout="vertical" name="misc_group" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
                </View>
                <View view_layout="vertical" name="ranged_group" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
                </View>
                <View view_layout="vertical" name="speed_group" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
                </View>
                <View view_layout="vertical" name="traderepair_group" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
                </View>
                <View view_layout="vertical" name="nanoaiding_group" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
                </View>
                <View view_layout="vertical" name="spying_group" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
                </View>
                <View view_layout="vertical" name="navigation_group" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)">
                </View>
              </ViewSelector>
              <VLayoutSpacer/>
            </BorderView>
            <BorderView view_layout="vertical">
              <View view_layout="vertical" name="statdetails">
                <TextView name="statName" font="HUGE" value="" layout_borders="Rect(2,0,2,0)" max_size="Point(10000,25)" min_size="Point(-1,25)" feature_flags="TVF_MULTILINE|TVF_WORD_WRAP|TVF_ALLOW_TEXT_SELECTION"/>
                <View view_layout="horizontal" >
                  <View view_layout="vertical" >
                    <View view_layout="horizontal" >
                      <TextView value="Base Skill:" layout_borders="Rect(2,1,0,0)" max_size="Point(130,-1)" min_size="Point(130,-1)"/>
                      <TextView value="" name="base" layout_borders="Rect(0,1,1,0)" max_size="Point(50,-1)" min_size="Point( 50,-1)" />
                      <HLayoutSpacer/>
                    </View>
                    <View view_layout="vertical" name="details1">
                      <View view_layout="horizontal" >
                        <TextView value="Buffed Skill:" layout_borders="Rect(2,1,0,0)" max_size="Point(130,-1)" min_size="Point(130,-1)" />
                        <TextView value="" name="buffed" layout_borders="Rect(0,1,1,0)" max_size="Point(50,-1)" min_size="Point( 50,-1)"/>
                        <HLayoutSpacer/>
                      </View>
                      <View view_layout="horizontal" >
                        <TextView value="Maximum skill allowed:" layout_borders="Rect(2,1,0,0)" max_size="Point(130,-1)" min_size="Point(130,-1)" />
                        <TextView value="" name="maxskill" layout_borders="Rect(0,1,1,0)" max_size="Point(50,-1)" min_size="Point( 50,-1)"/>
                        <HLayoutSpacer/>
                      </View>
                    </View>
                  </View>
                  <View view_layout="vertical" >
                    <View view_layout="horizontal" >
                      <TextView value="Current Improvement:" layout_borders="Rect(1,1,1,0)" max_size="Point(130,-1)" min_size="Point(130,-1)" />
                      <TextView value="" name="pointdelta" layout_borders="Rect(0,1,2,0)" max_size="Point(50,-1)" min_size="Point( 50,-1)" />
                      <HLayoutSpacer/>
                    </View>
                    <View view_layout="vertical" name="details2">
                      <View view_layout="horizontal" >
                        <TextView value="Cost to improve:" layout_borders="Rect(1,1,1,0)" max_size="Point(130,-1)" min_size="Point(130,-1)" />
                        <TextView value="" name="unitcost" layout_borders="Rect(0,1,2,0)" max_size="Point(50,-1)" min_size="Point( 50,-1)"/>
                        <HLayoutSpacer/>
                      </View>
                      <View view_layout="horizontal" >
                        <TextView value="Total cost:" layout_borders="Rect(1,1,1,0)" max_size="Point(130,-1)" min_size="Point(130,-1)" />
                        <TextView value="" name="totalcost" layout_borders="Rect(0,1,2,0)" max_size="Point(50,-1)" min_size="Point( 50,-1)" />
                        <HLayoutSpacer/>
                      </View>
                    </View>
                  </View>
                </View>
                <TextView name="statdesc" value="" layout_borders="Rect(2,5,2,0)" min_size="Point(100,62)" max_size="Point(10000,-1)" feature_flags="TVF_MULTILINE|TVF_WORD_WRAP|TVF_ALLOW_TEXT_SELECTION" />
                <VLayoutSpacer/>
                <View view_layout="horizontal">
                  <View view_layout="horizontal">
                    <TextView value="Remaining reset points:" layout_borders="Rect(2,1,1,1)" />
                    <TextView value="" name="rp" layout_borders="Rect(1,1,1,1)" />
                  </View>
                  <View view_layout="horizontal" name="resetView">
                    <Button label="Reset this skill" name="reset" layout_borders="Rect(0,0,0,0)"/>
                  </View>
                  <HLayoutSpacer/>
                </View>
              </View>
            </BorderView>
          </View>
          <BorderView name="autodist" view_layout="vertical">
            <TextView value="The automatic IP distribution has now completed.
            
You are welcome to do adjustments to the setup to better fit your wishes.

You have to save changes before exiting this window to keep your changes.

The following skills have been modified:"
 layout_borders="Rect(2,2,2,2)" max_size="Point(10000,-1)" feature_flags="TVF_MULTILINE|TVF_WORD_WRAP|TVF_ALLOW_TEXT_SELECTION"/>
            <View view_layout="horizontal" >
              <View view_layout="vertical" name="col1">
              </View>
              <HLayoutSpacer/>
              <View view_layout="vertical" name="col2">
              </View>
            </View>
            <VLayoutSpacer/>
          </BorderView>
        </ViewSelector>
      </View>
    </View>
  </View>
</root>
